Print in Order - Barrier
========================

Uses C++20 std::barrier for thread synchronization.

Build and test:
  $ bazel test --config=tsan //:foo_test              # Detects data races
  $ bazel test --config=asan --config=ubsan //:foo_test

Requirements:
  $ sudo apt install clang lld

Notes:
  - Clang configured as default compiler for better sanitizer support
  - UBSan vptr checking disabled (incompatible with ASan)
  - ASan and TSan are mutually exclusive
